===Power adapters=== The power adapters shown in the FCC photos are... *an '''OEM''' ADS012PM-W 120100 (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz, 0.5A -> 12VDC, 1.0A) *a '''Shenzhen Frecom Electronics Co., Ltd.''' F12W-120100SPAU L.P.S. (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz, 0.3A -> 12VDC, 1.0A)
